Appendix G: Energy Return on Investment (EROI) Detailed Bound

G.1 Derivation of Theorem 5

Theorem 5. Under the detachment condition and optimal frequency, \text{EROI} \ge \frac{\eta_{\text{opt}} \Delta \tau}{\kappa \tau_{\text{deposit}}} with \kappa = \frac{2\mu_s F_{\text{adh}} C_{\text{eq}} \tan\delta}{q k (1+\mu_s z/d_{\text{ins}}) \tau_p}.

